metadata.name: Uppoar #1
metadata.description: An inverted art experience produced in JavaScript driven in combination using machine learning algorithms and natural territory processing. Each NFT depicts a structure from a unique location in the form of code pouring upwards over the unique location denoted in the Metadata for your NFT. This NFT collection is a celebration of the beauty and diversity of our planet, and we invite you to join us on this journey of the natural and cyber world combined.
